The paper discusses the ontological query answering problem, which is a topic that falls under both database (cs.DB) and knowledge representation (cs.AI) communities. The paper also focuses on the complexity of the conjunctive query entailment problem, which is a topic that falls under computational complexity (cs.CC) and logic (cs.LO) sub-categories. Finally, the paper introduces a new class of rules and provides a generic algorithm for query entailment, which falls under the data structures (cs.DS) sub-category.
